==English==
===Noun===
'''vicariance'''
#(''biology'') The [[separation]] of a [[group]] of [[organism]]s by a [[geographic]] [[barrier]], resulting in [[differentiation]] of the [[original]] group into [[new]] [[varieties]] or [[species]]
#(''geology'') The geological event which produces such a barrier ([[volcano]], [[earthquake]], [[etc]])
